<title>&quot;BY GRACE ARE YE SAVED&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in lungsiet na'n,
 Hukdamna kim A siem;
 A lungsiet vangin A tela,
 Migilo hukdam di'n.

[V2]
 &quot;Lungsietna'n hukdam na hiu,
 Ginna'n, ginna'n, ginna'n nang tit ziek hilo in;
 Ginna'n, nang tit ziek hilo in,
 Nasep dawk... ahi puoi;
 Nasep ziek hileh mi uong ina Pathien thilpiek ahi
 Nasep ziek hileh mi uong ina Pathien thilpiek ahi
 Pathien thilpiek ahi (3) thilpiek ahi.&quot;

[V3]
 2. A Chapa Isu-ah,
 Pathien lungsiet a lang;
 Kross zahhuoi achun kikhai in,
 Pathien lungsiet A phuong.

[V4]
 3. A gingcha cheng kawmah,
 Krista chuh A kilak;
 Lungsiet na'n hukdamna a muu,
 &quot;Pathien chate&quot; ahiu.</lyrics>
</song>